<html lang="de">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>BBZ Projekt - Geräteturnen</title>
    <style>
      * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Arial,
      Helvetica, sans-serif; } body { color: #333; line-height: 1.6; } header {
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
      padding: 15px 50px; background-color: white; } .logo { height: 50px; }
      .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 30px; } .nav-links a { text-decoration:
      none; color: #333; font-weight: 500; } .user-icon { font-size: 20px; } /*
      Haupt CSS für die Seite*/ .main-content { padding: 20px 50px; max-width:
      1200px; margin: 0 auto; position: relative; } h2 { font-size: 32px;
      margin-bottom: 30px; color: #333; font-weight: bold; } .contact-section {
      display: flex; margin-bottom: 40px; } .left { flex: 2; margin-right: 20px;
      max-width: 500px; } .right { flex: 1; margin-top: 20px; } /*Kontakt Form*/
      .contact-form { background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 20px 100px;
      border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 40px; } .forms { text-align: left;
      margin-bottom: 20px; color: #444; font-size: 20px; } .form-group {
      display: flex; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 15px; } input[type="text"],
      input[type="email"], textarea { padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 4px; font-size: 14px; } .form-group input { flex: 1; }
      .full-width { width: 100%; margin-bottom: 15px; } textarea { width: 100%;
      height: 100px; resize: vertical; margin-bottom: 15px; } /*Karten CSS
      (Google Map)*/ .map-section { display: flex; gap: 20px; margin-bottom:
      40px; } .left_card { flex: 2; } .left_card iframe { width: 100%; height:
      300px; border-radius: 4px; border: none; } .right_card { flex: 1; padding:
      10px; } .right_card h3 { margin-bottom: 10px; color: #444; } .contact-info
      { padding-left: 20px; } .contact-info p:first-child { font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 5px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="main-content">
      <div class="background-triangle"></div>
      <h2>Kontakt</h2>

      <div class="contact-section">
        <div class="left">
          <p>
            Hast du Fragen zu unserem Verein oder möchtest du mal unverbindlich
            reinschauen, dann melde dich bitte vorgängig bei Sonja Nussbaumer.
          </p>
          <p>Wir werden uns so rasch als möglich bei dir melden...</p>
        </div>

        <div class="right">
          <div class="contact-info">
            <p>Kontakt</p>
            <p>Sonja Nussbaumer</p>
            <p>+41 76 455 88 48</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-form">
        <h3 class="forms">Kontaktiere uns</h3>
        <form action="">
          <div class="form-group">
            <input type="text" placeholder="Vorname" />
            <input type="text" placeholder="Nachname" />
          </div>
          <div class="email">
            <input
              type="email"
              class="full-width"
              placeholder="E-Mail Adresse"
            />
          </div>
          <textarea placeholder="Deine Nachricht"></textarea>
          <button class="button">Senden</button>
        </form>
      </div>

      <h2>Karte</h2>
      <div class="map-section">
        <div class="left_card">
          <iframe
            src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d5410.8618674171985!2d7.631225800000001!3d47.305919300000006!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x4791d10cd0dd084b%3A0x91ede35d0db489e8!2sGartenstrasse%202%2C%204713%20Matzendorf!5e0!3m2!1sde!2sch!4v1745926149642!5m2!1sde!2sch"
            allowfullscreen=""
            loading="lazy"
            referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
          >
          </iframe>
        </div>
        <div class="right_card">
          <h3>Adresse</h3>
          <p>
            Sporthalle Matzendorf
            <br />
            Gartenstrasse 2,
            <br />
            4713 Matzendorf
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <img src="/img/Buchstabe/k.png" alt="" class="background-letter" />
  </body>
</html>